data.description: Move in ready!!  Adorable 3 bedroom 2 bath home in Southwest Village.  Walk into the spacious living room and enjoy the gorgeous hardwood floors.  In the kitchen you will find plenty of cabinet space and a large island.  All kitchen appliances stay.  Main floor laundry and full bath that has been remodeled.  3 nice sized bedrooms and another full bath complete this bright and cheery home.  Some recent updates include texture and paint throughout, 2 remodeled bathrooms, newer blinds, updated flooring, and shelves in garage.  Attached garage.  Out back is a huge, fully fenced backyard with a patio and mature trees.  Skyline school.  Close to schools, churches, and shopping!  Call for your showing today!
